title: [Fethayl Bog, Cypress Grove]
description: Ascending into the sky, a cypress dome blocks out nearly all of the sun's rays with their broad branches.  Grey, somber fog clings to the ground persistently, adding to the uniform dreariness of the area.  Through the bleak greyness, the land dips into a small depression to the southeast, while higher land remains unsubmerged.
